<div style="float:left; width:6em;text-align:left;">
<div class="noprint plainlinksneverexpand navbar" style="background:none; padding:0; font-weight:normal;&#160;;background: #EEDD82;border:none;; font-size:xx-small;"><a href="/wiki/Template:Nebula_Award_Best_Novel_1981-2000" title="Template:Nebula Award Best Novel 1981-2000"><span title="View this template" style=";background: #EEDD82;border:none;">v</span></a>&#160;•&#160;<a href="/w/index.php?title=Template_talk:Nebula_Award_Best_Novel_1981-2000&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Template talk:Nebula Award Best Novel 1981-2000 (page does not exist)"><span title="Discussion about this template" style=";background: #EEDD82;border:none;">d</span></a>&#160;•&#160;<a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Template:Nebula_Award_Best_Novel_1981-2000&amp;action=edit" class="external text" title="http://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Template:Nebula_Award_Best_Novel_1981-2000&amp;action=edit" rel="nofollow"><span title="Edit this template" style=";background: #EEDD82;border:none;;">e</span></a></div>
